name: Usha Ramani Vemuru
bio: I am an ed-tech entrepreneur from India extremely passionate about helping people and making a difference. I love travelling and also run communities for Google in my home town Visakhapatnam. I navigate the roles of a boss lady, community organiser and a family woman. With every event, we help local developers learn, share, connect, collaborate and enhance their opportunities in the tech domain.

name: Sampath Balivada
bio: Building intuitive and engaging (customer, developer, user, visual) experiences is my Ikigai.

name: Manas Malla
bio: A student, designer, and developer with experience in over 45+ languages and frameworks over the last 6+ years. Built over 10+ sustainable solutions, 35+ apps and 56+ UI designs. Building solutions is my ikigai #BeingAForceForChange. My journey has been fueled by a desire to create experiences that are both functional, engaging, intuitive and accessible, empowering individuals and communities. I am always striving to push the boundaries of what's possible with technology.

name: Swapna Dande
bio: I'm a curious mind, always exploring new horizons. I'm passionate about harnessing the power of AI and ML to create innovative solutions that make a positive impact. As a WTM Ambassador, I'm dedicated to empowering individuals and communities through technology. A fearless traveler, I believe in breaking barriers and empowering women to reach their full potential. Let's connect and inspire each other!

name: Satish Karnatakapu
bio: An ardent follower of APJ Abdul Kalam whom he passionately idolizes, he draws inspiration from the work ethics of Steve Jobs. He is unswervingly working towards instituting a better society with happier humans. He is a social entrepreneur and an innovator, who flagged off Vizag Volunteers, as a project under Kalam Dream Labs to serve the poor and needy and is dedicated to making our city and the world at large - a healthier and a happier place to live.

name: Kavya Chandana
bio: A problem solver who uses his creative talents to tackle design-related challenges. With a keen eye for detail and an innate understanding of infographics, visual design, and UI/UX. I am able to transform complex information into visually compelling and user-friendly designs. Whether it includes working on a brand-new project or revamping an existing design.

name: Chandan Khamitkar
bio: A developer and student pursuing Bachelors in Computer Science Engineering. Experienced in over 19 languages- frameworks with over a year experience building rich experiences as a Full-Stack Web Developer. Interned at Ati Uttam (a SAAS based company)

name: Jayadhar Ummadisingu
bio: Passionate about Machine Learning, I enjoy solving problems, learning new technologies, and creating impactful solutions. Eager to grow and contribute to tech.

name: Revanth Peethala
bio: Passionate about solving real-world problems, exploring machine learning and its derivatives and eager to apply my skills in a dynamic, growth-oriented environment.
